caption.p: Snapshot of the HDO Performance of 15%Ni/Nb 2O 5 Catalyst in the Recycling Experiments

van Krevelen plot comparing the H/C and O/C molar ratios for the lignin oil, residue fraction soluble in methanol, and liquid products obtained in the presence of 15%Ni/Nb 2O 5 catalyst and from the control experiment (no added catalyst).
